Package: RSI
Title: Replicative Significance Index (RSI) and RSI*
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Suhrud", "Panchawagh", , "panchawagh.suhrud@mayo.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Vinay", "Suresh", , "vinay.suresh@bnc.ox.ac.uk", role = "aut"),
    person("Bhavik", "Bansal", , "bhavik.bansal@utsouthwestern.edu", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Computes the Replicative Significance Index (RSI)—the
    proportion of hypothetical replications that achieve statistical
    significance—plus a skewness-adjusted variant (RSI*). Includes
    plotting utilities and simulation helpers.
